Step-by-Step Execution Guide

Pre-Migration Checklist

 Environment assessment completed
 OCI compartment and network configured
 Security groups and policies applied
 Backup procedures validated
Cutover Procedure
Day of Migration - 4 Hour Window

Hour 1: Pre-Cutover
Stop new transactions on source
Final data synchronization
Health check of OCI environment
Hour 2: Application Cutover
DNS switch to OCI load balancer
Application server validation

Database connectivity test
Hour 3: Testing & Validation
Functional testing
Performance benchmarking
User acceptance testing
Hour 4: Go-Live Decision

Performance metrics review
Rollback decision point
Production handover
Rollback Procedure
Switch DNS back to source
Verify transaction integrity
Incident post-mortem
